<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <style>
    body { font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, sans-serif; color: #1a1a1a; line-height: 1.6; }
    .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; }
    code { background: #f3f4f6; padding: 2px 6px; border-radius: 4px; font-size: 14px; }
    pre { background: #1f2937; color: #e5e7eb; padding: 16px; border-radius: 8px; overflow-x: auto; font-size: 13px; }
    .key-box { background: #eff6ff; border: 2px solid #3b82f6; border-radius: 8px; padding: 16px; margin: 16px 0; }
    .key-value { font-family: monospace; font-size: 14px; word-break: break-all; color: #1e40af; }
    h2 { margin-top: 24px; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <h1>Your CloudPricing API Key</h1>

    <p>Hi <%= @api_key.name %>,</p>

    <p>Your API access request has been approved. Here's your key:</p>

    <div class="key-box">
      <strong>API Key</strong><br>
      <span class="key-value"><%= @token %></span>
    </div>

    <p><strong>Save this key now.</strong> It won't be shown again. If you lose it, you'll need to request a new one.</p>

    <h2>Quick Start</h2>

    <p>List LLM models:</p>
    <pre>curl -H "Authorization: Bearer <%= @token %>" \
  <%= @base_url %>/api/v1/llm_models</pre>

    <p>List cloud instances:</p>
    <pre>curl -H "Authorization: Bearer <%= @token %>" \
  <%= @base_url %>/api/v1/instances</pre>

    <p>Filter by provider:</p>
    <pre>curl -H "Authorization: Bearer <%= @token %>" \
  "<%= @base_url %>/api/v1/instances?providers[]=aws&vcpus_min=4"</pre>

    <h2>Endpoints</h2>
    <ul>
      <li><code>GET /api/v1/instances</code> — Cloud instances (filterable)</li>
      <li><code>GET /api/v1/instances/:id</code> — Instance detail</li>
      <li><code>GET /api/v1/llm_models</code> — LLM models (filterable)</li>
      <li><code>GET /api/v1/llm_models/:id</code> — Model detail</li>
      <li><code>GET /api/v1/providers</code> — Cloud providers</li>
      <li><code>GET /api/v1/llm_providers</code> — LLM providers</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Rate Limits</h2>
    <p>100 requests per minute. Check <code>X-RateLimit-Remaining</code> in response headers.</p>

    <p>Happy building!<br>CloudPricing</p>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
